<https://saref.etsi.org/saref4bldg/Building> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A building represents a structure that provides shelter for its occupants or contents and stands in one place. The building is also used to provide a basic element within the spatial structure hierarchy for the components of a building project (together with site, storey, and space)."@en .
